{"tid":2082364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳俄羅斯下令懸賞阿富汗美軍 拜登痛批川普毫無作為","createTime":"2020-06-28T03:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T20:11:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"16bdbee4e4fd13e0a4142686505d5c9ef7c548de","tid":2082364,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕《紐約時報》報導，俄羅斯軍方暗中與阿富汗神學士（又譯塔利班）的激進份子聯繫，對美軍為首的聯軍下達懸賞令，美國總統川普知悉這項情報，卻沒有採取報復行動。對此，民主黨總統參選人拜登（Joe Biden）痛批川普毫無作為。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透》報導，拜登表示，《紐約時報》揭發了令人震驚的內幕，尤其是川普沒有採取報復行動，「他不僅沒有對俄羅斯這種嚴重違反國際法的行為施以制裁或任何後果，川普還繼續在普廷面前表現出敬重和自我貶低，種種這些令人尷尬的行徑。」拜登說，如果他擔任總統，將會對俄羅斯進行報復。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3210988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3210988&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=b4f1d2d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3210988&h=d9c8444c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3210988</a>"},{"pid":"d08ab04b57f29d24c49fc8ae4337288a624fa749","tid":2082364,"uid":343361,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"生意佬講就兇狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但拜登做更6撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51c0775a5a5b2ac17b4509c6c11ee72312a0a8b","tid":2082364,"uid":24140,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"反正阿富汗都撒緊軍<br />\n有咩野咪比哂俄佬同支那玩<br />\n<br />\n一去到敘利亞搞事，以色列自會做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79677afdc0ab6af8bb0dc1f6a8752da1281e607","tid":2082364,"uid":150610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"戀童癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00f9f670a4